text: Cercopithecine betaherpesvirus 5 (CeHV-5) is a species of virus in the genus Cytomegalovirus, subfamily Betaherpesvirinae, family Herpesviridae, and order Herpesvirales. African green monkeys (Chlorocebus spp.) serve as natural hosts. == References == Category:Betaherpesvirinae
title: Cercopithecine betaherpesvirus 5
